title: SOUTH PARK  SNOW DAY! Official Release Date Trailer
description:
SOUTH PARK: SNOW DAY! is coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox X|S, Nintendo Switch, and PC on March 26, 2024!

From South Park Digital Studios comes the next chapter in the journey of the New Kid. A massive blizzard has thrown the town into chaos and, more importantly, cancelled school.
